<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ د ن:</span> <span class="c2">(هَادَنَهُ)</span> صَالَحَهُ وَالِاسْمُ <span class="c2">(الْهُدْنَةُ)</span> .<span class="c5"> وَمِنْهُ قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> هُدْنَةٌ عَلَى دَخَنٍ أَيْ سُكُونٌ عَلَى غِلٍّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>